data.oai_dc:dc: Nexus file containing 938 genes for 19 taxa. See Taxon_list.txt for names of each taxon, this is a nucleotide nexus file with a CHARSET that defines each gene. Gene names correspond to gene numbers in the Insecta HMMER v3-2 core ortholog database. For further information on these genes see Supplementary Table 2 from Breinholt and Kawahara 2013.
